race.description: Footts Swan Hill Demolition Group Mdn Plate
race.comment: DURHAM (9) has switched from James Cummings and off a wide barrier came from the rear beaten 2.3L at Horsham first-up. Impressed gelded and is sure to be better for it. Yendall stays aboard and he should relish the step up to the mile. YATCHAW (7) improved again finding a place at Ballarat over a mile. Hits this contest at peak and rates to be right in the finish. SAKER FALCON (3) is third-up and ready to show more for the sharp Hayes yard.  Better suited at country level and he has the pace to be in a prominent position from the outset. Should get every chance to run out the longer journey. VALDA WARRIOR (11) showed plenty early doors but has been struggling to find that form. Draws inside today and sits on the limit. Has been racing in stronger and may fill a slot in this line-up.
